  "detailed_description": "A psychological horror game developed by only one person, with what he had in hand, a not very good machine, but made with all the dedication.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1464350/extras/81c839429bad9ce6c2700efdc6088a61.avif?t=1673224925\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>After some time, after the accident that you caused, in which it cost the life of your wife and children, you live the life of Josh, a normal person, but after that, everything changed in his life, Josh blames himself for what he committed, and consequently, it affected in a way. You start to witness paranormal events at your residence, and your goal is to try to find out why these events are occurring.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1464350/extras/2f593ee0499cc21e0708382728e8f449.avif?t=1673224925\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A horror game where events take place chronologically, that is, they are always moving around the house.<br><br></li><li> A short game in which your theme will draw your attention every minute during the game.<br><br></li><li> Atmospheric Terror</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "A psychological horror game developed by only one person, with what he had in hand, a not very good machine, but made with all the dedication.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1464350/extras/81c839429bad9ce6c2700efdc6088a61.avif?t=1673224925\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>After some time, after the accident that you caused, in which it cost the life of your wife and children, you live the life of Josh, a normal person, but after that, everything changed in his life, Josh blames himself for what he committed, and consequently, it affected in a way. You start to witness paranormal events at your residence, and your goal is to try to find out why these events are occurring.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1464350/extras/2f593ee0499cc21e0708382728e8f449.avif?t=1673224925\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A horror game where events take place chronologically, that is, they are always moving around the house.<br><br></li><li> A short game in which your theme will draw your attention every minute during the game.<br><br></li><li> Atmospheric Terror</li></ul>",
